  "name": "Fireburst Chamber",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>A fireburst chamber allows you to direct the detonation of a grenade inside of a grenade launcher or an undermounted grenade launcher.</p><hr><p><strong>Activate—Fireburst Mode</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (manipulate)</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The grenade launcher or the undermounted grenade launcher gains the area (cone) trait with a range of 15 feet and uses the properties of the grenade it fires instead of using its normal range. You can end this effect with an Interact action.</p>"
    },
